## 4. Check

Validate the gtsummary output against a hand computation.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
dat |>
  group_by(species) |>
  summarise(
    n = n(),
    mean_mass = mean(body_mass_g),
    sd_mass   = sd(body_mass_g),
    .groups = "drop"
  )
```

